[normal]Examination of Witnesses[bold]Witnesses:
[normal] 
[normal]Gillian Guy[bold], Chief Executive, Citizens Advice, 
[normal]Martin Lewis[bold], moneysavingexpert.com, 
[normal]Peter Tutton[bold], Head of Policy, StepChange, and 
[normal]Richard Lloyd[bold], Executive Director, Which?, gave evidence.
