[normal]t just needs to be slower
[normal]. 
[normal]It needs to be slow
[normal]er to allow time to reconsider, and while there is a cooling-off period you pay interest if you decide to change your mind, so you are effectively still getting the loan. W
[normal]ithin affordability, 
[normal]you have the controls that need to be put on the lender, but then, to allow the individual
[normal] to take 
[normal]some more control of their own af
[normal]fordability, the instantaneous, high-technology nature of the way these operate is very dangerous. It is a feeding mechanism, very close and akin to gambling
