[normal]This all flicks ba
[normal]ck to your earlier question to m
[normal]e, about the difference between trying to do everything to make sure people do not repay, and being willing to lend to people you are going to get to repay when they cannot afford it
[normal]. 
[normal]If you have got the CPAs working in the right way, and people have £10 in their bank account and every day you are doing a CPA for £10 on a fishing expedition, people are going to repay
[normal]. 
