[normal]I gather, Minister, you wish to respond.
[normal]Jo Swinson[bold]: Absolutely
[normal]. 
[normal]It was helpful that the industry indicated that they wanted to clean up their act and have their own charter, which they created last summer
[normal],
[normal] and 
[normal]that
[normal] came into force last November
