[normal]; t
[normal]hat is just the way the world works, but you would expect to find the majority broadly compliant
[normal]. 
[normal]We did not find that
[normal]. 
[normal]That was the big trigger that said to us that there was something wrong with this market
[normal]. 
[normal]We were concerned that, actually, non-compliance is a competitive tool in this market
[normal]. 
