[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q155 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Mr Walker:[bold] I do think it is an important area to engage, and to try
[normal] to
[normal] make sure 
[normal]that 
[normal]we have as much control as possible to protect 
[normal]UK
[normal] consumers
[normal]. 
[normal]Just moving on from that, we have talked a lot today about affordability, and obviously the sector’s charter itself talks a good game on affordability but it is not something that appears
[normal], 
[normal]particul
[normal]arly from the OFT investigation, 
