[normal]It is a very fast
[normal]­
[normal]moving industry.
[normal] 
[normal]It has grown hugely in the last few years, and one of the difficulties around the sometimes cumbersome nature of putting legislation in place is the time that it takes from the consultation point to actually getting legislation in place
